      "value": "<p>The blade of this <em>+1 greataxe</em> bears a design of a human skull.</p>\n<p>Whenever a creature damages you with an attack, the skull changes its appearance to look like the face of that creature. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your next damage roll against that creature before the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>Because the face reshapes each time you're damaged, you get the additional damage only if you attack the creature that damaged you most recently.</p>"
